[code]/RANGE/
public void arrowchecking() {
if(UseBow){
inCombat();
teleportToX = absX;
teleportToY = absY;
CheckArrows();
CheckArrowtype();
CalculateRange();
if(arrowtype == 1) { //Bronze
hitDiff = misc.random(playerMaxHit) + misc.random(1);
arrowgfx = 10;
}
else if(arrowtype == 2) { //Iron
hitDiff = misc.random(playerMaxHit) + misc.random(2);
arrowgfx = 9;
}
else if(arrowtype == 3) { //Steel
hitDiff = misc.random(playerMaxHit) + misc.random(3);
arrowgfx = 11;
}
else if(arrowtype == 4) { //Mithril
hitDiff = misc.random(playerMaxHit) + misc.random(4);
arrowgfx = 12;
}
else if(arrowtype == 5) { //Admanant
hitDiff = misc.random(playerMaxHit) + misc.random(5);
arrowgfx = 13;
}
else if(arrowtype == 6) { //Rune
hitDiff = misc.random(playerMaxHit) + misc.random(6);
arrowgfx = 15;
}
else if(arrowtype == 7) { //Fire
hitDiff = misc.random(playerMaxHit) + misc.random(5);
arrowgfx = 17;
}
else if(arrowtype == 8) { //Ice
hitDiff = misc.random(playerMaxHit) + misc.random(5);
arrowgfx = 16;
}
else {
hitDiff = 0;
}
}
}
public void CheckArrowtype()
{
if(playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 882){
arrowtype = 1; // bronze
}
else if(playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 884){

}
else if(playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 886){

}
else if(playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 888){

}
else if(playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 890){

}

arrowtype = 7; // Fire arrows
}
else if(playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 78){
arrowtype = 8; // Ice arrows
}
else if(playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 2866){
arrowtype = 9; // Flighted ogre arrow
}
}
public void CheckArrows()
{
if(playerEquipment[playerWeapon] == 4212 || playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 882 || playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 884 || playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 886 || playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 888 || playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 890 || playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 892 || playerEquipment[playerWeapon] == 4214 || playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 598 || playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 942 || playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 2533 || playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 2535 || playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 2537 || playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 2539 || playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 2541 || playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 78 || playerEquipment[playerArrows] == 2866){
